15472.description: Sacred sword that can neutralize Freya's power. Cannot use it directly due to some unknown M. Atk.

15473.description: Obtained from Tunatun on the Beast Farm, this whip will enable the bearer to control tamed pets. Must be equipped to use. Beast Training - Accompany

15474.name: Golden Spice
15474.description: Feed used to tame baby animals on the Beast Farm. Using this feed will allow the monster to drop adena and/or items, but will give less experience. Golden Spice

15475.name: Crystal Spice
15475.description: Feed used to tame baby animals on the Beast Farm. This feed will cause the monster to give more experience, but no adena or items. Crystal Spice

15476.name: Blessed Golden Spice
15476.description: A better quality feed that has a chance to tame animals on the Beast Farm with just one application. Blessed Golden Spice

15477.name: Blessed Crystal Spice
15477.description: A better quality feed that has a chance to tame animals on the Beast Farm with just one application. Blessed Crystal Spice

15478.name: Golden Spice (S-Grade)
15478.description: A better quality feed that has a chance to turn Beast Farm babies into fully grown pets with just one application. Using this feed will allow the monster to drop adena and/or items, but will give less experience. S Grade Golden Spice

15479.name: Crystal Spice (S-Grade)
15479.description: A better quality feed that has a chance to turn Beast Farm babies into fully grown pets with just one application. This feed causes the monster to give more experience, but no adena or items. S Grade Crystal Spice

15480.name: Old Golden Spice
15480.description: Old and unusable Beast Farm Feed

15481.name: Old Crystal Spice
15481.description: Old and unusable Beast Farm Feed

15482.name: Golden Spice Crate
15482.description: This box hold up to 50 Golden Spices. When converted, there is also a chance that Special Feed will be received. Golden Spice Capsule

15483.name: Crystal Spice Compressed Pack
15483.description: Small pack with a compressed Crystal Spice. When you use it, it changes into 50 Crystal Spices. Special Feed may also come out. Crystal Spice Capsule

15484.name: High-level Angel Circlet
15484.description: High-level Angel Circlet. Uses 2 hair accessory slots. Blessed Escape skill can be used. Blessed Escape

15485.name: Torch

15486.description: Energy from the Seed of Annihilation resides within these Spirit Stone Fragments. Can be used at Special Product Broker Kirklan.

15487.name: Maguen Plasma Collector
15487.description: This device is used to collect plasma from the Wild Maguen that inhabit the Seed of Annihilation. Under the right circumstances, plasma collection allows you to obtain a pet Maguen. Maguen Machine

15488.name: Maguen Pet Collar
15488.description: Necklace that summons a Maguen. The summoned Maguen can eat wolf-type feed, and it takes away some of the experience points the Pet Master earns. No exchange, drop, sale, or mail available. Wolf's Necklace

15489.name: Elite Maguen Pet Collar
15489.description: Necklace that summons an Elite Maguen. The summoned Maguen can eat wolf-type feed, and it takes away some of the experience points the Pet Master earns. No exchange, drop, sale, or mail available. Wolf's Necklace

15490.name: Maguen Collection Box
15490.description: Its contents are a mystery. The only way to find out what is inside is to open it.

15491.name: Elite Maguen Collection Box
15491.description: Its contents are a mystery. The only way to find out what is inside is to open it.

15492.name: Sel Mahum Salmon Porridge
15492.description: Sel Mahum salmon porridge. Smells better than expected but not by much. Salmon Soup

15493.description: Pouch containing the spores of Fantasy Mushrooms, which grow in the Plains of the Lizardmen. Detailed information can be obtained from Investigator Sally on the Plains of the Lizardmen.

15494.name: Sticky Mushroom Pouch
15494.description: Pouch containing the spores of Sticky Mushrooms, which grow in the Plains of the Lizardmen. Detailed information can be obtained from Investigator Sally on the Plains of the Lizardmen.

15495.name: Vitality Plant Leaf
15495.description: Leaf of the Energy Plant, which grows in the Plains of the Lizardmen. Detailed information can be obtained from Investigator Sally on the Plains of the Lizardmen.

15496.name: Seer Ugoros Pass
15496.description: Document from Investigator Johnny in the Plains of the Lizardmen that verifies you possess the required skills. It indicates that you have the right to go and see Tanta Lizardman Seer Ugoros. Show it to Gatekeeper Batracos near the Plains of the Lizardmen.

15497.name: High-Grade Lizard Scale
15497.description: The highest-quality Lizardman Scale without any blemishes obtained after defeating Tanta Lizardmen Seer Ugoros. Take it to Researcher Ankumi on the Plains of the Lizardmen.

15498.name: Middle-Grade Lizard Scale
15498.description: The medium-quality Lizardman Scale obtained after defeating Tanta Lizardmen Seer Ugoros. Take it to Researcher Ankumi on the Plains of the Lizardmen.

15499.name: Vial of Tanta Blood
15499.description: Vial containing the blood of Tanta Lizardmen. Take it to Investigator Laki on the Plains of the Lizardmen.
